                        <header>
                                          <h1 class="nodeTitle">
                GAO: American Naval Officers Still Too Tired; Only 14% Getting Adequate Sleep
              </h1>
                            <div class="nodeInfo">
                <div id="nodeAuthorInfo">
                  

                  By <a id="CBAuthor" href="/user/65">Susan Jones</a>

                  
                  | May 28, 2021 | 5:21am EDT

                </div>

              </div>
              <div class="nodeButtons">
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-6">
                    <div id="audioSynth">
